      <title>花旗家族办公室客户削减现金以进行风险更高的投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/citi-s-family-office-clients-trim-cash-pile-to-make-riskier-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团的家族办公室客户正在减少现金持有量，以投资风险更高的资产类别，反映出他们对金融市场日益乐观的前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/citi-s-family-office-clients-trim-cash-pile-to-make-riskier-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
